snippet.title: Cattails | Nintendo Switch™ Trailer
snippet.description:
Cattails is coming to the Nintendo Switch™ eShop on November 29, 2018! Press release: http://cattailsgame.com/pressrelease_10_23_18

Presskit: http://cattailsgame.com/presskit/sheet.php?p=cattails

Want to know more about Cattails? Visit our website at http://cattailsgame.com

Cattails on the Nintendo eShop: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/cattails-switch

Buy Cattails today on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/634160/Cattails__Become_a_Cat/

Play Cattails on Steam? Don't worry, we haven't forgotten about you either! v1.2, a Technical Update, is available now. We've also got a small content update scheduled before the end of 2018.

Trailer created by Devon House Creative: https://www.devonhousecreative.com/
